
Top Pairs on US: https://help.ftx.com/hc/en-us/articles/360048135772-Uniswap-Index

This list was generated by: Ordering Uniswap (Matic) pools by liquidity 


Validations:
============

IsTokenApproved (both tokens need to be approved)
IsTransactionPending
CurrentGasFees
CheckTransactionSuccess => take txnId and verify status on blockchain

If 3 transactions fail in a row, stop the Robot

Add a counter to matchingPairs => if for 5 times we are below ?% diffPercent, stop fetching prices for that pair


