Test Query:
===========

{
pairs(first:100, orderBy:trackedReserveETH, 
  orderDirection:desc)
{
  #id
  token0{symbol}
  token1{symbol}
  token0Price
  token1Price
  #reserveUSD
  #trackedReserveETH  
  #volumeUSD
}
}


